\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Mother usually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your father ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes, but - of course mother was there more than what he was with him being out all - well, at work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 About how often to you remember being punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You were a good girl were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, well you had to be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember any particular occasion when you were punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I can't remember any occasion, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember how you felt about being punished, did you just accept a smack and being sent up to bed as being fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, I accept it but I used to be - me pride used to be hurt very much so. Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Would you say that you received the ideas you had about ho
w to behave from both your parents or did one play a more important part than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
No, I don't think one did, I mean - my father was very kind and very good and so was me mother, no, I wouldn't - put one in front of the other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 When you had a birthday would it be different from and other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, used to have a birthday party.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Who used to come to your birthday party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well my girl friends, from the school I imagine, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How many did you used to have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh maybe half a dozen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you have anything special to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh-yes, used to have jelly and trifles and things like that, that was your treat.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you have presents on your birthday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 From your parents and from your family as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Can you remember anything }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  did with your mother and father together on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Yes, we used to - after we'd opened our parcels - of course they used to open them through the middle of the night, used to come down and 
have breakfast. And then we all used to sit round the fire, mother would get the dinner going and then we'd all sit round the fire and - play with our things and show each other what we'd got. Have a real happy time. Then we'd have our meal. And then we'd
 just do the same, roasting chestnuts and things like that in the fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Was there anyone in the family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. Oh me. Oh a little bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You used to sing at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 To entertain the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, oh yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What sort of things did you sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Oh - I couldn't tell you know. Well of course in those days you made your own entertainment didn't you. Yes, I remember I used to entertain them. And 
my brother - father used to join in, the boys wouldn't We used to have a proper family entertainment. Oh we had some happy times, very happy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What else did you do for family entertainment like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well suppose wed sit and play snakes and ladders and ludo, 'cos I mean they were - going as early as that so that's what we'd be playing.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Just you singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Without a piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your brothers join in this as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 If they were in they would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever play any outside games with the family, when you went to the park?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Just with a ball. Kick the ball about. Such as that. Cricket probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were there books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were there newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Now I wouldn't like to say about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember your mother or father reading, you said your father read to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your mother do any reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I don't think so. I don't think she would have much time.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did they ever read aloud to you, you say your father did sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 In bed, yes, when you used to go to bed my father u
sed to read or - if mother had time she would - she'd put you to bed, she would read but - she hadn't always the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did they ever read aloud to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember what sort of books there were in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well a lot 
they would read to me would be the - nursery rhymes and nursery stories. But - the older boys used to go to the library so I don't know what they would - get.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you belong to the library too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes. Yes. Oh yes. Yes, I used to belong to the library and I - I don't know what sort of books I got out but - I used to }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 enjoy}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  reading them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember a funeral in the family while you were a schoolgirl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes. My grandfather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember who went or anything at all about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 We all went. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Can you tell me anything about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Yes, I can remember going to the house and - they carried the coffin out and of course we all followed and - and we went to the cemetery and I remember the - the service and the chur
ch. And this - at the graveside. And then we went back to the house and we had something to eat. Then of course we had to go in the back out of the road and the grown ups stayed in the front - in the room - front room. Then when they were ready to go away
 we all - went away. That's what I can remember about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you wear any special clothes for the funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. I had a blooming white panama hat. Big - big swathe of black satin ribbon round and a great big black rosette at the front. And I d
on't know what coat I had on but that hat always sticks in my crop. White panama hat with this great swathe of black satin ribbon, black satin rosette stuck in front, dear me. What a climax. Oh dear.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How old would you be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh I'd be about six then. Oh that hat, I'll never forget it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you know who else went to the funeral, did lots of families go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, yes, all the family, it was a big family, they were all there, all the sons and daughters and - grandchildren, oh yes, there w
as quite a crowd.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were you taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relations at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Relations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Who usually took you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well that used to be - the weekends we used to go out }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 \endash }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 \lquote cos}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
 I'm talking about the two younger ones, not the two older ones. We used to go out every - if it was fine on a Saturday afternoon or Sunday afternoon - for a walk. And nine times out of ten we}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7214847\charrsid12133122 \rquote d end}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  up at my grandfather's. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did he live near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Not far away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Who took you for the walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh - mother and father and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Your mother and father and two younger children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, two younger, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were you taken shopping at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Just on a Thursday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Pay day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes - no, but they used to go for the groceries. And of
 course in those days you had to carry everything. And I used to go with her to - help to carry the basket. We used to wait 'til - me father had come home, had his tea, he used to wash up while her and I went. Of course shops used to stay open long hours 
in those days. And - Co-operative stores we used to go to and she used to get all the week's groceries. And I used to help her to carry them home, that's about the only time - bar running to the corner shop to spend your ha'pennies}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  your pennies - on your own of course. And I never remember going for that. I must have gone sometimes or other but I can't remember that.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What time of the year did you have new shoes and where did you buy those from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well - in the co-operative again, 'cos oh me mother was dead keen on Co-operative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were your shoes always new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Or were they ever secondhand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. Oh no. Always new.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What time of the year would you have new shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I suppose when you were ready for them, I don't k
now. I don't know that they bought them - a certain time. I suppose when you were ready for them you would buy them. But I know we all had two pair each. Weekdays and Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 These were the Sunday shoes that you had to clean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 'Cos in those days they were put away. They weren't used - only for Sundays. Eeh - when you think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever go out with just your father, you said he used to take you out on Sunday mornings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you go anywhere else with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well, no, just to the park and places like that. No, that's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember any other outings with your parents, Bank holidays or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, used to go down to - Redcar. Oh we used to go down to Redcar two or three times. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Just for the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Just for the day, yes. I don't ever remember going to stay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How would you get there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Train.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever go away for a holiday at all do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 I used to 'cos I used to go and stay with my
 other grandma, Middlesbrough. I used to go and stay there for all the school holidays - all the long - the summer holidays. Yes. Used to stay there. Every year, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 That would be about three or four weeks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well whatever - how long the school holiday was, three or four weeks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did the rest of the family ever get a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Yes, the - 'cos they had a lot of relations and - they used to go and stay with various ones. Oh yes, we had got a holiday. I don't ever remember mother and father g
o. But - the family, they all used to get - a break. Oh yes. Yes, we had relations all over England. They used to put up with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What did you do when you were on holiday, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, I had a lot of girlfriends and I used to - play in 
the road - skips, jumps, hopscotch, walk to the park, play on the roundabouts and such as that. Then of course Sunday was a day of rest and you had to behave yourself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days? You said you went out Saturday mornings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, - Saturday - Saturday afternoon we used to go out. Sunday morning - Saturday morning, oh I should imagine we'd just play round about.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 And Saturday afternoon you used to go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Used to go out - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 And usually finish up visiting a relative did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did you spend Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well we used to go to - church in the morning and Sunday school. And church at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Three times a week?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Which church was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 St Luke's. 
St Luke's - Church of England, yes. But if there was anything good on at the Salvation Army we used to go to the Salvation Army at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 The whole family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh no, no. Just my - meself and my friends. Used to be - just concerts you know, band con
certs and things like that. And where we lived was quite near. The - Salvation Army barracks. And we just had to go round the corner to it you see and of course it was generally good on a Sunday night. Used to go round and - go there instead of going to c
hurch. Of course it was quite open, mother and father knew we were dong it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 But you thought it was more interesting than church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well it made a change. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you have different clothes for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How long did you keep them as Sunday clothes, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I suppose 'til they - were getting a bit on the shabby side and then we'd take them down and get new ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 They were always your best clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh always your best clothes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you play games on Sunday at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. Eeh no, had to sit and read.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No games at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your parents think it wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How often did they go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Mother used to go every Sunday night. But my father just - now and again he used to go, but still he used to go. He used to see we went.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your mother go Sunday morning as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 She just went Sunday evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were there any Sunday school outings that you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, you - while event - event of the year, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Where did you used to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh used to - go out - well was the country in those days but it isn't today. 
Piercebridge way, up there, of course you were in - miles away from home when you were there. Used to have a big field and used to be a big tent up. Oh yes, used to - highlight of the Sunday school outing was that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What did you have to eat on these outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well you know what they had at - Sunday school }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 tea parties}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 Buns}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
, iced buns and things, oh I remember those iced buns. Oh dear me. We used to sit on long trestles - in this tent. If you - you used to get a bag with these cakes and things in. And if you didn't like any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 throw}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  them right under. Oh happy days, eeh man, they were good days were those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What happened at the end of the afternoon when all the food was under the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well of course we went out and - nobody could say who put 
it there you see. Eeh, some fun. It used to be a - a shop called Beadles that they used to get - all these things from and we used to call them }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 Beadle\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  bags. Oh dear me, eeh, when you think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were there any other Sunday school outings at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I think we just had that and the parties Christmas time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 This was just a Sunday school party you had was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Can you tell me anything about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, well I suppose we'd - we'd have jelly and stuff like that at Christmas party. And cakes and things. Play games.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What other social activities organized by the church did you take part in, did you belong to anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, they used to have - a Band of Hope.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What was that exactly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well it was like - us
ed to go and used to sing hymns and - play games and things like that, was more or less - like what the youth centres do today isn't it. I mean, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 only}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  we used to sing hymns.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How often did you go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 And - well just the once a week. Used to cost a ha'penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did the church run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 None that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you belong to any other club organized by the church or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I can't remember it being said. But - you daren't get from the table 'til you'd asked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were you taught to say your prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, by }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 Jove}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  yes. We were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, now and}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122  a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 gain, not - Sunday nights mainly.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Who used to say them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well me - sometimes my father, sometimes me mother, oh yes, we used to have those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, not really. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, he was a Conservative, he was - he was a big man in the Conservatives but he didn't take any actual part in anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What did he do for the Conservatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well if there was a Conservative meeting he would go and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 attend}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  it. But - I can't remember him doing anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Have you any idea why he held those views, why he was a Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I think he thought people with money - could rule a country better than those that hadn't, I think that used to be his idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Why was that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I don't really know. Suppose it - maybe his father before him was one, I don't know. 'Cos it does run like that doesn't it. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 And your mother's political views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, she was a very strong Conservative, more s
o than my father really. And she used to - they used to have some - meeting on an Afternoon through the week because she used to go and oh she was very keen on Conservatism.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you know why that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, no, no, I - couldn't say why.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What did they do at these meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Now I couldn't tell you, I suppose it's been social affair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do your}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122  remember}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  your father voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I can't say I do. Suppose he would do.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember your mother voting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 But if they did vote it would have been Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh definitely, by }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 Jove}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers, do y
ou know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember your father working for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember your mother working at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Just these afternoon meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I couldn't say about me father, he was maybe mending the shoes. Mother used to do a lot of sewing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 That's all you remember it?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 That's all I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your mother have any interests outside the home, you say she went to these Conservative meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 That's all she had, yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I think the highlight used to be the shopping on Thursday night. And she used to meet all her friends there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 It'd be about quarter past five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 He didn't go out at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your father attend any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. He used to like a drink of beer on the house and that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your father take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Football, he used to see - go and watch football but other than that he didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did he attend the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did he bet at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your mother attend any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did you get on with your brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Well, we all thought a lot of each other but - with me being younger than the two eldest of course they thought I had to do everything they wanted me to do
 and - of course I used to - stick up for myself you know in no uncertain way. There used to be some right battles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You actually fought did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh - yes, Sunday dinner time when we used to be having this bottle of pop. You know if you shook the
 bottle when you took the cork off, went - the cork used to be cork corks in those days. Loose them }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 \lquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
cos it used to fly all over. And we were having - we were all sat at the table anyway and - something was said to me, it was something about the gravy. And
 I let fly, shook - got hold of this bottle of pop and I shook at and I pulled the cork off - and it went all over the ceiling. Eeh - what a Sunday dinner that was. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 Eeh}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  I'll never forget that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you finish your dinner or did you have to leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
No, no, I was sent upstairs. No, I didn't get any dinner that day. But - you know they thought they were boss over me and I thought they weren't and - that's how we used to go on. But the youngest boy - we used to have a bit of a tussle togethe
r but - other than that we were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Was there any one brother that you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 felt}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, the younger one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 As a child who did you play with, you mentioned some girl friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, used to have a lot of girl friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you play with your brothers at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Girl friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Any particular girlfriends when you were at a school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, oh yes, there was one, her father was a tailor. And he used to have - they liv
ed in a - biggish house and he had one of the rooms as a tailor's workshop. And oh it used to be lovely if we could go in there and watch him and he had one or two men working for him, go in and watch them cutting out and using the great big irons and suc
h as that you know. You - it used to be lovely to stand and see these great sewing machines you know. Oh it used to be the highlight of the day to go and watch them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you play with any neighbours at all, did the girl live near you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 She lived quite near, yes, oh there was quite a few girls we used to play with but this one in particular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you play with any neighbours at all in the street?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How do you mean - children? Oh yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Where did you normally play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 In the street. Or we lived near North Lodge Park, we used to go into the park a lot and play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You said you went to the girl's home, did you play in your own home, did you bring your friends in just to play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Anywhere else you played apart from in the street or park or home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember what games you played when you were out with your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well, it'd be - skipping - checks, I remember we used to play, is it checks, checks where you go like that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 with}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
 a bowl - yes, checks. And - hopscotch, itchy bay we used to call it. And skipping. Itchy bay. Itchy bay. It's like hopscotch, they call it hopscotch now. You know, you mark the squares, yes, that's right, yes. We used to call it itchy bay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were you allowed to bet dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well was told we hadn't to but we nearly always did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You got away with it did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Providing they were - respectable people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your parents discourage you from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Well they would just say - oh I wouldn't play with so and so if I was you. That's all - they didn't compel you, you know, didn't say, you've not got to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 They just suggested it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you know why they didn't want you to play with certain children?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I - they must have had some reason for it but I can't think why.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember who the children were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, yes, I can remember them. Well 
I don't think they were just up to - I mean we were very ordinary people but still I don't think they were just up to our standard. No, I think that was the reason.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You mean they were rougher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I don't mean - they were just as - clean as what they could have been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, no. No, just the - Band of Hope.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you have any hobbies when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 I do - used to do a lot of embroidery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What sort of embroidery, wool embroidery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
No, silk embroidery. And I used to do crocheting. I don't ever remember knitting in those days. I used to - I used to do the fancy work a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What sort of things did you embroider?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Tray clothes. And chair backs and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you still do it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No, what I do now is knit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you keep any pets when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 I didn't. But the boys had the guinea pigs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you collect anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you do any gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You left that to the boys did you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever go for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you go for long walks at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I mean - you walked to the South Park you'd gone a long way then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever go bicycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, no. No, I'd left school before I got a bike.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 When you went for walks, you said you went with your father and sometimes with your mother, did you ever go with anyone else for walks?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I don't think so. Can't remember doing so. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 
I mean, in those days you - you hadn't to go very far. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you go to any theaters, concerts, music halls or cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, the - cinemas but just if it was anything - suitable. You hadn't to make a habit of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Who decided if it was suitable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I suppose me mother or me father would do so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 So you didn't go regularly to the cinema?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you go to any theatres, concerts or music halls at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I can't remember.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember how much you got?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes, I used to get sixpence a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 That would be a lot on those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 It was, but I had to bank fourpence. I only had tuppence left, but still tuppence we a long - a lot in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You got this every week did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What were you saving up for with your fourpence?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh I don't know, but it just had to go in the money box.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did you spend your tuppence?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Used to buy ha'porth - ha'porth of this and ha'porth of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Sweets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, sweets. Licorice and stuff like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after her house or family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 I suppose if one of us were poorly one of my aunties would come and help her. But that would be all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Would any friends or neighbours ever help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh they could have done, we had some very good neighbours, very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 But that would only be in a case of illness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 If your mother was ill or confined to bed how did she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I suppose one of the neighbours would see to us and then me father would see to us when he came home.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You don't remember any particular occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No. I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember what happened when your younger brother was born, he was only a little bit younger than you, you probably won't will you?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh - he was born when I was four. No, I can't
 remember. I remember I had to wheel him in his blooming pram. Wheel him in his pram. Remember that. But that's all I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your parents have any relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes. My father's relatives - mother's lived at Middlesbrough but - me father's all lived round about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 All in Darlington?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 All in Darlington, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How much did you see of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I used to see them in his - his father - his mother and father - my grandfather and grandmother every Sunday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How often did your parents see their relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well they used to do a lot of visiting in those days because there wasn't much else you did in - was there, not in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How much times a week would they see relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh I wouldn't like to say. Just - well very frequent really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Where did they usually meet their relatives, in the homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 In the home, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 And your mother's relatives were at Middlesbrough, how often did your parents see their relatives at Middlesbrough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Mother used to go once a fortnight. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your parents have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Where did they see their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Just in each other's houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your mother and father share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, oh yes. Well they'd be husband and wife.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your mother have friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Just the neighbours and those that - she met at - she went to the - Conservative meeting. I don't remember any specific friends, of course - neighbours in those days were - friends really weren't they. More so than now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your father have friends of his own at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, not really, I think that they - they both sort of - were kind of with the couples more or less. No, 'cos he wasn't a man that
 went out you see. He was proper family man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were friends ever invited into the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember how often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh I wouldn't like to say how often but - oh yes, they used to come, they used to bring their family and we used to go - to their house.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Would they be offered anything to eat or drink when they came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, we'd have a meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Would it be any particular day or occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I think it was just - have a walk round sort of style. Drop in, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Would you say that the friends invited in were your mother's friends or your }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 father\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  friends or friends of both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Of both I should say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did friends call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh they - ladies, yes. Because we lived - mor
e or less at the centre of the town. I mean, if they were out shopping they could just pop in.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 A good stopping place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your neighbours pop in without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Any particular time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh no, just when they felt like it I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Your parents visited friends didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did they ever visit neighbours together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I suppose they just stand talking at the doors to them, I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 People often tell us that in those days they made their own amus}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 e}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 ments, what do you think your }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 parents}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
 did when they got together with their friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you know I wouldn't like to say. I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You don't remember whether they had music or games or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well they wouldn't have music 'cos we hadn't anything in the house. No, I wouldn't say - I should imagine they'd just sit talking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups, in that time before 1918 di
d you think of some people belonging to one and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I don't think so. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Could you tell me at all what the different classes were in this area in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well of course there was the - there was the poor children.
 And I should say we were middle class and - I can't remember any upper class, not while - round about where we were anyway. There certainly used to be some poor ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Which class would you say you belonged to yourself, you said the middle class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Middle class I should say.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What sort of people belonged to the same class as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well people just like ourselves I should say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What sort of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well there was this - there was one was a painter and decorator and busin
ess for himself, there was the tailor. And - the other one was a jeweler.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What sort of people belonged to the poorer classes you've mentioned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well - it was the children that their father's wouldn't work and - wasn't the children's fault, it was their father's fault.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you find quite a lot of families where the fathers wouldn't be bothered to work to support them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, not a lot. Not a lot. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, no. I don't. We hadn't to make any distinction at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were you ever told to curtsey or show respect in some way to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Was there anyone you called sir or master or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in these ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 In the district who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Pease's I should imagine. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Any other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 There was Havelock-Allen. Havelock Allen. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you come to contact with them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you know why they were considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well they both had - a lot of business connections in the town.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What about the shopkeepers, do you know who they associated with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, no, no, I wouldn't like to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did the clergy have any particular friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How do you mean? Going visiting or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Who did they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh well, where we went to he used to associate with everybody. Didn't matter what they were. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Who do you think the teachers had as friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I couldn't really say, I mean, the teachers as far as I knew, they were all - friendly with each other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No other particular group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you know anything about the farmers, who did they have as friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh I wouldn't like to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 And employers, the management at the North }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 Food}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  Shops, did you ever notice who they had as friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, we never came in contact with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What sort of people would you say went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well - all classes of people really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 And who went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well a lot of our friends went to chapel. They were just the same as us, mixture I should imagine.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Where you lived did all the people in the middle class have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 Well the - people that we were friendly more or less with were the same as ourselves. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 But as I say, the poorer people, well they had a lower class - of living altogether. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Could you describe a family in this poorer sort of class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Well - their father - father wouldn't work and of course the mother hadn't the money to carry on with and - suppose they used to - they were very shabby in clothes, I don't kn
ow what they're - about their food, but they used to be very shabby in clothes. There used to be one or two families, but - that's about all I could say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you think that one group felt itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I think you find that all over don't you. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were some families thought of as rough and some as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 There's one family lived again}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 st}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  us, they were very rough, but of course they had a lot of boys. And - the father was a - a rough sort of a man and of course the boys were. That's about the only one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Not so far as I know. Not as }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 far as}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, they treat them just the same. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Was it possible at that time to move from one class to another and can you remember who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well of course where we lived you knew who you were friendly with they were all our - the same as us, so like I couldn't really say.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well, there was one or two round about us that you could say - were real gentlemen and real ladies.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Well, this - this one that was a tailor he was - of course he'd been a military man and he was - he was a proper gentleman really. In all his ways. And there was another person, the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 jeweller's
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  wife, she was really what you would call a proper lady. I mean, not in a snobbish way but in a - nice way. That's the only two I can think of as - more or less just as we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 More by manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, the police station was right she end of our street. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What did you think of the policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh they were grand lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You got on well with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 When you were naughty did your mother ever say, I'll call a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Well I can't remember and I don't think she would because with living so near we knew all and we were all so friendly that I don't think she would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did you think the policemen treated the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh they were friendly with us all, yes. Oh they were grand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Rented.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you see anything of the landlord at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. I don't know how the rent was paid, I don't ever remember seeing a landlord.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember feeling that your parents had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No I don't think so. They weren't - overburdened with money but still they were comfortable.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What difference did it make to the family when your father was ill or out of work, was he ever ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 He was never out of work. And the only illness he had was just before he died. He never was ill before. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever get help from the guardians or the parish or any charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
When there was someone in the district whom the people disapproved of very strongly was there any special way in which they showed it? Do you remember anyone being made to leave by rough music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember anyone being show in that way that they were disapproved of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh no, there was no need, no, no. The only thing you would do - would be ignore them, that's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No demonstration?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were you given lessons by one of your parents, a tutor, or a governess?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 When you first started at three did you do a full day or just half a day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. No. Full day. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What time of the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Nine o'clock would be - yes, nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you come home for lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 When did you go back again in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Half past one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 And what time did school finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 That was a long day for a little girl of three?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 It was a nice little school, it was - in Kendrew Street. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Where the Buffs are now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. It was the Civic - wasn't the little theatre lately? Yes, yes, yes. That's where I went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How long did it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh - about ten minutes, maybe not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did anyone go with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 I used to go with me brothers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 With having older brothers you'd be well looked after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You said you came home for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 I didn't like it at first but then I got like it. Then when I got older I didn't like it again.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You didn't like it when you first started because it was new to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Why do you think you learnt to dislike it afterwards when you got older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh I don't know, I - you go through these phases don't you. No, I can't think why. No, I can't think why but I - just didn't like it.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 So on the whole would you say you liked school or you didn't like school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh on the whole, yes, on the whole, yes, I would like - say I would like it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh I liked all the teachers. Yes, yes. There was one a Jewess, she - oh she was lovely. She was really a lovely teacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I don't think so, I think they just - taught you the three - what is it, the four R's - three R
's or something, reading, writing and arithmetic. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did they put any stress on good manners or tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes. Yes. I mean - you had to show your clean hands on a morning and your clean shoes. Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did they stress punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, definitely, yes. And obedience, punctual and obedience, yes. But still, on the whole, school wasn't too bad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How about ways of speaking, did teachers emphasise?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, you had to - speak properly and you hadn't to - slur your wo
rds or anything, you had to speak properly. As properly as you could anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 If you did something the teachers disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well you would get a smack across your hand with a cane. Cane, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did the girls get the same punishment as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 As the boys, yes, only the boys used to get theirs on the bottom.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 For what sort of offences were you punished at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well, disobedience I should imagine. About all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did they ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did they ever visit the school? Meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Of course there wasn't parent teachers like there is the present dime. It would be a case of if - they called
 for you or took you or something like that they would see the teacher in those days, but I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 don\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
 think other than that they would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 This Miss - Lazarus used to single me out because she said I had a good voice, it should be trained. But - that's the only thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you remember any other children being singled out by the teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I can't think of anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Well there would be but with us - being girls, suppose we weren't in them quite so much, the boys would be more in that line wouldn't they. I mean in those days - children weren't so rough as they are now. I mean, you - daren't be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You must notice a big difference when you look around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh you're telling me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, yes, yes. Childr
en who - you thought weren't clean and such as that. But looking back, really it was very unfair to do that wasn't it, they couldn't help it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 But you mostly went by cleanliness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, yes yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you go on to another school afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I stayed there all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No I don't think so. -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you attend any part time education afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, I went to evening classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What did you take at evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Eeh now I couldn't tell you. Just general subjects I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How long did you carry on going to evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Not very long. Eeh no I was hopeless. I was going - supposed to be going to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 night school}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 . Used to go out with me books but that was it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Where did you go instead?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh I went out with a boy. Oh dear. Oh dear. I was for it when I was caught out. Yes, they sent a letter from the Education, why hadn't I 
been attending. End of that romance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What did they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh well, I'd to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 stay}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  in you see. Then when - the evening classes I was taken there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 They made sure you went then after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Eeh, happy days.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No I don't think so. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you think you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 benefitted}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh definitely, yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 While you were at school did you have any part time jobs or any means or earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you do a job at all before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 I went to work in a shop. And I didn't like it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How old would you be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I'd be just turned fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 That'd be 1915 then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 '15. Yes. So then I went to work in a - wholesale warehouse. Silk stockings and underwear and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 In a wholesale warehouse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Was that before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, yes. This'd be about 1915.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 So you weren't a shop assistant very long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
No, no, no, I didn't like it. Then I went to work in this wholesale warehouse. And I started as a junior and I was the manageress when I left to get married, yes, so - I came up, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 So in 1918 you'd still be in the wholesale warehouse?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes, I was still in that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Have you done any other jobs since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes, just - after my husband died I was - I was at home on me own for so long and then I went to work in the schools, helping with the 
meals. Yes, I had five years there and I quite enjoyed it to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you help to prepare them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No, service - no, must - just serve the dinners out. I used to enjoy, meeting children and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How long ago was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Five - five years. Since it finished, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Thinking of your main occupation, would you have preferred another type of occupation or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I don't think I would, I was very happy there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you serve an apprenticeship or training period for any of your job
s, you really had your training period as you worked your way up didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. No, I had no training, no, just as you say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you belong to any trade union or professional organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well where I was the - they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 treat}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  you as an equal. Oh very much so and - they used to take us up to the house - to their house - Christmastime and - I won't say it was a party but we used to have a meal. And i
n the summer they used to take us - for a day out into the country.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 The whole staff?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. They were - used to close the place up and take - oh yes they were very good, he - they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 treat}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  us as an equal, I don't know about other places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you feel that there were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 divisions}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  of interests among workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well some - how do you mean?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers, did you feel that or not?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Not where I was. Not where I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 So you were just one big family really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
Just what we were really, yes, yes. Majority of them went there from leaving school and only finished when they were married. Oh it was a grand place to work it was. I don't know whe
ther you know it or not - Goldsworthy, have you seen them advertised in the - they're in Gladstone Street now. Yes, well I was there when they first started. Not in Gladston}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 
e Street, they used to be - in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Anson Square. Of course - I used to work for their father. Then when the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid553125\charrsid12133122 so}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  was old enough he came in the business but - his father and mother, oh they were marvellous people. Oh they were wonderful people to work for.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 When you were manageress what were your duties, what did you have to do really, what were you responsible for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well - the - the stock and customers that came in, you had to see to them. And also the invoicing. And see that the goods got away.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 It must have been very interesting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh it was very interesting, used to meet a lot of nice people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, I wouldn't say so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you continue to live at home after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did it change your relationship with your brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes - no, I don't think so. Maybe I got a bit more respect from them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you spend your Sunday any differently now when you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well you certainly - I don't remember going to Sunday school but I know I had to go to church night and morning. Oh yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you yourself take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 I didn't, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you have any particular view?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I used to be Conservative and I think it was just because my parents were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 And what was your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 He was Conservative. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you vote in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever feel under any pressure from anyone to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Were you a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you ever work for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 I didn't, my husband did but I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 But that would be later on after 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Oh yes, definitely, yes.
