\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 When I first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987598\charrsid12133122 started}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122  I had to - help to unpack the stock. Put it in the fixtures. And get orders up, put orders up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did you get this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well the manageress is a friend of - my mother's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 So you got it through your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What hours did you work at the warehouse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Nine 'til five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you have a lunchtime off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Do you work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you work on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 'Til dinnertime, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Was that the only half day on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Half day Saturday.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you have any holidays with pay from the warehouse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Not at the first - few years, but later of course I did get paid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How much holiday did they give you at the beginning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 You told me you started off at ten shillings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you have any rises before 1918 do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Oh yes. Yes, I got - so much each year. Half a crown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you feel that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I did, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Did you give any of this money to your mother or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Well I gave her it all for so long. Then of course as I got older - I just gave her so much for the - keep.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What would you spend the rest on?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 What was it spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Sweets. I do love sweets - and other small personal things. The rest my mother had to pay for my keep.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did you get on with the people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Very well, we were a grand crowd and I became very friendly with the girls I worked with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did your employer treat you and how did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 Very well indeed. 
I knew his wife and family and I was treated as part of the family. Most of the people who worked there started when leaving school and stayed until married. We were one big happy family. I looked on him as a friend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8862850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 How did you feel about the work, did you like or dislike it?
\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\s15\qj \fi-461\li461\ri0\sa240\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid8862850 \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10314797 LV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4015237\charrsid12133122 
I didn't care for it at first but soon grew to like it. I didn't like unpacking the big skips - it was difficult to reach the bottom so I used to dodge this work. As I got promoted it became easier. By 1918 I had moved up f
our places so I could pick and choose the jobs I did and had more control.
\par }}